{
  "stem": "9995.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I went to a camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came already to the city one day after the war started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He ran away as soon as-- I didn't see him since June 1939.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was breadwinner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you see, the minute they came in-- my grandfather was very wealthy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they closed all the bank accounts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They call it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took the money out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So whoever was saving and had mainly money was completely destitute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now my mother immediately lost her job because this was also an Austrian firm called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were making the famous locks, elevators, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, the guy who was actually fixing the elevator became the boss.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother's boss ran away to Romania.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were to have gone with him if it wouldn't be for the fact that I was in the camp and took a few days with trains going in different directions to come to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later on, we still could have run away, but we didn't know how bad it's going to be because it wasn't like that in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my mother and her sisters were saying, we cannot leave the furniture and the carpets and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And because of this, we did not run away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was still a possibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, what was good in our case was that my father was a jeweler, and my mother had a lot of jewelery, which she was selling throughout the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- but she also had other means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because people had to write petitions to get an apartment and to get a job and whatever, and my mother had her typewriter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So she was writing it and was actually making some money.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
